SQL_STMT_U.val: select CMON_YEAR, CMON_MONTH, cast(sum(CMON_TOTAPAYCR) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(CMON_TOTABALMUTCR) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESMAN) as decimal (13,2)) , cast( sum(CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESAUTO) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum (CMON_TOTADEDUCTCRALLDISC) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTADEDUCTCRNOTALLDISC) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(CMON_TOTADEDUCTCROTHER) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESMAN) as decimal (13,2)), cast( sum(CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESAUTO) as decimal(13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTAPAIDINV) as decimal (13,2)), cast( sum(CMON_TOTAPAIDINVXDAYSFROINVDAT) as decimal (17,2)), cast ( sum(CMON_TOTAPAIDINVXDAYSFRODUEDAT) as decimal (17,2)), cast(sum(CMON_LIQRATIO1) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(CMON_LIQRATIO2) as decimal (13,2)) from :1 where CMON_ADMNO = :6 and CMON_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and CMON_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO and CLNT802_TRADECATEGORYHELLER = :2 and CMON_YEAR between :3 and :4 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':5' group by CMON_YEAR, CMON_MONTH order by CMON_YEAR, CMON_MONTH for fetch only
